    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The philosophical study of religion, especially concerning the rationality of religious beliefs, and the descriptive analysis and elucidation of religious language, belief, and practice.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
